sine-demo

This is a repo for learning C, kinda...

tse
---

print scrolling sine wave centered in terminal

Build:
    $ make tse

Usage:
    $ ./tse.sh <terminal width>

Hotkeys:
 * f / r = increase / decrease wavelength
 * d / e = half / double delay between printed lines
 * q     = quit


ste
---

print an elipse in standard terminal window (80x24) w/ ANSI colors

Build:
    $ make ste

Usage:
    $ ./ste

